CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

January 6, 2014

[Cite as 01/06/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-7.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1833. Fed. Home Loan Mtge. Corp. v. Koch.

Geauga App. No. 2012-G-3084, 2013-Ohio-4423. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal.

Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to strike appellant’s notice of appeal and memorandum in support of jurisdiction, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.

It is further ordered by the court that appellee may file a memorandum in response to jurisdiction within 30 days from the date of this entry.
